---
title: Quick Beef and Noodle Stir-Fry with Snow Peas and Peppers
description: Stir-fries are a delicious go-to for a quick weeknight dinner, but make sure you have your pan up to heat and all your ingredients nearby for optimum speed and tastiness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-beef-and-noodle-stir-fry-2eb6291c.jpg
